# Read `.ai/AGENTS.md` Before Coding

Before making any code edits in this repository, first read `.ai/AGENTS.md` in the current session and follow it as the primary local guideline.

If `.ai/AGENTS.md` has not been read yet in this session, do not proceed with file edits until it is read.
